data.text:
Episode 16

Among the guests on Graham's sofa are Dame Judi Dench and Sir Kenneth Branagh, world heavyweight boxing champion Anthony Joshua, Swedish star Noomi Rapace and actor and comedian Greg Davies. Also featuring music from Claire Richards.

Episode 13

Together on Graham's sofa tonight: Oscar-nominated actress Keira Knightley and actor-director Kenneth Branagh, talking about new movie `Jack Ryan'; French football star Thierry Henry; comedian Lee Mack; and music from Katy B.

Episode 2

Hollywood legend Robert de Niro, and Oscar-Winning co-star Anne Hathaway from the new movie, `The Intern'. Director and actor Sir Kenneth Branagh also joins Graham on the sofa.

Episode 6

Graham Norton is joined by Judi Dench and Kenneth Branagh, who star in the new movie version of `Murder on the Orient Express', Johnny Depp, Michelle Pfeiffer and Josh Gad. Plus music from St Vincent, who performs the single `Los Ageless'.
